00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:37,900
Elephant?

563
00:19:38,070 --> 00:19:38,770
What brings you here?

564
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:52,330
Zhi?

565
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:53,940
Zhi?

566
00:19:56,510 --> 00:19:57,330
Stop pressing it.

567
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,330
