571
00:20:08,310 --> 00:20:09,050
We can't just

572
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:10,180
break into her house.

573
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:11,490
Let's go.

574
00:20:11,510 --> 00:20:12,380
You know Zhi must be

575
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:13,090
