576
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:13,940
What if she has

577
00:20:14,030 --> 00:20:14,940
an accident inside?

578
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:16,050
We need to go in and check.

579
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:17,220
Can't you say

580
00:20:17,270 --> 00:20:18,330
